snippet.title: Quizwitz - Trailer
snippet.description: QuizWitz is a party quiz game that allows you to use your smartphone, tablet or any other smart device as a game controller. You simply collect your own rounds and quizzes on the social platform, or create and publish your own. Buying QuizWitz on Steam will grant you a lifelong Premium account on the social platform.
